X
\sin X + \cos X  \ge 1
(\sin X + \cos X)^2 = 1 + 2 \sin X \cos X
\sin X + \cos X \ge 1
x
\sin x
\cos x
\sin x
\cos x
2\sin x\cos x\ge 0\\ 1+2\sin x\cos x\ge 1\\ \sin^2x+\cos^2x+2\sin x\cos x\ge 1\\ \left(\sin x+\cos x\right)^2\ge 1
\sin x+\cos x\ge 1
X
